		</a>
	</div>
</footer>
<style>
	footer {
		padding: 3em 1em 6em 1em;
		background: var(--bg-darker);
		color: var(--text-secondary);
		text-align: center;
		border-top: 4px solid var(--balatro-red);
		border-bottom: 2px solid var(--balatro-blue);
		margin-top: 4em;
		box-shadow: 
			inset 0 4px 0 rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.3),
			inset 0 -2px 0 rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.3);
	}
	
	.social-links {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		gap: 1em;
		margin-top: 1.5em;
	}
	
	.social-links a {
		text-decoration: none;
		color: var(--balatro-blue);
		transition: all 0.1s ease;
		padding: 0.5em;
		border-radius: 0;
		border: 3px solid var(--balatro-blue);
		box-shadow: 3px 3px 0px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.4);
	}
	
	.social-links a:hover {
		color: var(--balatro-red-bright);
		border-color: var(--balatro-red-bright);
		box-shadow: 
			4px 4px 0px rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.5),
			0 0 10px rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.5);
		transform: translate(-2px, -2px);
	}
</style>
